 Service-now.com
 
 Description: 
 Allows for the modifications of task_time_worked values to update the task timer field. 
 Typically the timer is self controlled based on a cumulative value so changing a task time worked value will make the task timer appear inaccurate.
 Requires setting property 'com.snc.time_worked.update_task_timer' to true

 The BR has modified the OOB version in plugin Service Management Basics [com.snc.service], zeroing the time worked when no time worked [task_time_worked]
 records are found. If the original functionality is required please remove the second parameter passed to updateTaskTimer, or set it to false.
**/

